WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Here is the Acme Notes demo. Let me open the editor.

2
00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:09.500
I type a note and click Save. It says saved, but nothing persists on reload.

3
00:00:09.500 --> 00:00:15.000
The toolbar icons are very light gray on white. Hard to read.

4
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:20.000
On a narrow window the sidebar overflows and covers the text.

5
00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.000
That is the end of the walkthrough. Three items to fix.
